data.description: Nestled in the heart of East Kyle within a quiet cul-de-sac, this inviting house offers comfortable living, a prime location, and endless possibilities. Boasting tasteful cosmetic updates and a well-thought-out open floorplan, this single-story gem ensures a balanced living experience. HVAC is only 3 years old and the foundation has been given a clean bill of health (inspection report is available)! On one side, the primary ensuite provides a peaceful retreat, while on the opposite side, two additional bedrooms and a full bathroom offer convenience. The expansive, pie-shaped backyard and patio present a blank canvas awaiting your creative vision, all within a non-HOA neighborhood that grants the freedom to utilize and personalize your property. Enjoy the convenience of proximity to Tobias Elementary School and a variety of retail shops and restaurants, with easy access to I-35 for both Austin and San Antonio.
